title: Closure of the Token Swap
body:
DAWN governance proposal #2 - Voting on which date we will close the token swap for the protocol.

We announced our token swap last year. Now we’ve completed the migration of over 71.99% of the network according to Etherscan and special thanks to our community and partners who helped us accomplish this. As the last step of the network migration process, we would like to invite the community to participate in the decision making for the final date.
Proposal

Selecting a date to close the token swap in the future.

You need to choose which date you want this window to be closed:

Choice #1: 3 months from April 14th, 2021
Choice #2: 6 months from April 14th, 2021
Choice #3: 9 months from April 14th, 2021
Choice #4: 12 months from April 14th, 2021

To vote

You need to withdraw your tokens from a cryptocurrency exchange to an Ethereum wallet that supports DeFi, like MetaMask
You need to have tokens in your wallet before 14h of March
The voting window is between 14th March and 14th April
Voting itself is not going to cost anything

Read the voting instructions here 
(https://dawn.org/post/how-to-vote-on-dawn-token-governance)

Voting Incentive

Dawn team is going to airdrop 150 tokens to the first 100 voters and then 100 tokens to the additional 100 voters as the reward for participating in early community governance efforts.

150 DAWN for 1st -100th Voters
100 DAWN for 101st - 200th Voters

How to get Dawn tokens

If you do not have any Dawn tokens yet, you can purchase them. After your purchase, remember to withdraw your tokens to MetaMask. 
Remember to swap your 1ST tokens

If you are holding old 1ST tokens you need to swap them to Dawn tokens before you can use them.


我们在2020年中宣布了将1st转换至Dawn的计划，截至目前，Etherscan上的数据显示已有71.99% 的1st成功完成转换。在此再次衷心感谢社区成员和相关机构的协同合作。作为转换工作的最后步骤，我们在此邀请用户进行投票来决定转换工作的最后截止日期。

方式 

选择转换的截止日期：

从4月14日起3个月
从4月14日起6个月
从4月14日起9个月
从4月14日起12个月

如何投票

你需要将Dawn存入支持DeFi的以太钱包，例如MetaMask，可用钱包列表
以上步骤需在3月14日前完成
投票期限为，3月14日 - 4月14日
投票不会产生费用
投票网址

奖励机制

作为早期参与社区治理的奖励，团队将向前100位参与投票的用户空投150Dawn，向接下来参与的100位用户空投100Dawn。

投票奖励
标准
150 DAWN
第1至100位用户
100 DAWN
第101至200位用户

如何获取Dawn

非持币用户可以在中币，BigOne，Bkex等购买Dawn，然后将其存入以太钱包，例如 MetaMask。
